# {{†}} a kind of [[macaque]], probably the [[rhesus macaque]]
#* {{zh-x|當 其 時 也，山獸 驚躍，水禽 亂 飛，魚 獺 沉潭 以 不 動，獑 猱 拱 樹 以 相{xiāng}依。|Just at that time, the beasts in the mountains leapt in fear, and the fowl in the waters flew in confusion; the fish and the otters drowned and did not move, and the '''macaques''' and gibbons swung around the trees and relied on each other.|CL|ref='''7th–8th century''', {{w2|zh|趙冬曦}} (Zhao Dongxi), {{w2|zh|s:三門賦（有序）|三門賦|pref=《|suf=》}}}}
#* {{zh-x|瘦 去 形 如 鶴，憂 來 態 似 獑。|Meagre as a crane; anxious as a '''macaque'''.|CL|ref='''9th century''', {{w2|zh|皮日休}} ({{w|Pi Rixiu}}), {{w2|zh|s:江南書情二十韻寄祕閣韋校書貽之商洛宋先輩垂文二同年|江南書情二十韻寄祕閣韋校書貽之商洛宋先輩垂文二同年|pref=《|suf=》}}}}
